>    ============================================================ */
. di as result "================================================"
================================================

. di as result " 4 x 4 SUMMARY: post-treatment coefficient (se)"
 4 x 4 SUMMARY: post-treatment coefficient (se)

. di as result "================================================"
================================================

. di "Estimator | mm_protests        mm_violent         mm_nonviolent      mm_g
> vr"
Estimator | mm_protests        mm_violent         mm_nonviolent      mm_gvr

